race.description: Racing Qld Supports Safety In Racing Hcp (Bm60)
race.comment: The well-related REGGIE'S FOLLY (1) (half to G1 winner Heavens Above) got a well-deserved victory over this course and distance last time out and will have taken a bunch of confidence from that win. Winning rider Hamblin sticks in the stirrups and maps perfectly for this contest from gate two. Rates the testing material. ECHO HUNTER (8) has been thereabouts at the past few efforts and gets some weight relief with the claim. Ready to show her best now. Former Victorian SOMETHING FORJO (11) hasn't been too far away in all four starts since joining the new stable and looks a must for the multiples. DROP THE PILOT (6) is improving with racing this preparation and may earn some minor money. BATTLESPACE (7) next best from the inside alley.
